# TXT2EPUB

A simple tool for converting TXT books into ePub.

## Installation

```shell
pip install txt2epub
```

## Usage

You may convert a file from the command line:

```shell
txt2epub convert -i <input> -o <output>
```

...or using the GUI:

```shell
txt2epub gui
```
